                   rdfs:comment "[jSymbolic M-18] Fraction of melodic intervals that are octaves."@en ;
                   rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://purl.org/ontology/mrc/> ;
                   rdfs:label "Melodic Octaves (M-18)"@en .


###  http://purl.org/ontology/mrc/melodicPerfectFourths
