###  http://purl.org/ontology/mrc/releaseDecade
mrc:releaseDecade rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                  rdfs:domain mrc:Track ;
                  rdfs:range wd:Q39911 ;
                  rdfs:comment """Links an mrc:Track to an instance of wd:Q39911 (Wikidata: decade)
representing the decade in which the track was released. The decade value
is derived from the MSD release year field (mrc:msdYear). Rather than
redefining 'decade', this property reuses the Wikidata class wd:Q39911
directly as its range. Relevant Wikidata properties on decade instances:
  - wdt:P31  (instance of)      → wd:Q39911 (decade)
  - wdt:P361 (part of)          → wd:Q6927 (20th century) or wd:Q6939 (21st century)
  - wdt:P155 (follows)          → the previous decade (e.g. wd:Q34653 → wd:Q34052)
  - wdt:P156 (followed by)      → the next decade (e.g. wd:Q34653 → wd:Q2002)
Example: a track released in 1994 links to wd:Q34653 (\"1990s\")."""@en ;
                  rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://purl.org/ontology/mrc/> ;
                  rdfs:label "Release Decade"@en .


